Legacy nodded both to Tuscon as well Perceptor, "I will warn them of
your change in factional allegiance."  Legacy said to Perceptor as he
hefted Rodimus into a comfortable carrying position, and then with a
slight push into the air he began to lift up into the air, his anti
gravity emitters holding both he and Rodimus as they pushed upwards.

Meanwhile from up above voice could be heard calling down into the
pit, "HEY MAXIMALS! It's me CHEETOR and RAMULUS and AIR HAMMER!"
Cheetor's familiar voice could be heard. We're working to get you guys
out!"

(TAG)

Preston
